        "id": "APPOINTMENT",

          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Fill this form and book your appointment",
                  "type": "TextSubheading"
                },
                {
                  "height": 220,
                  "scale-type": "contain",
                  "src": "",
                  "type": "Image"
                },
  
                {
                  "type": "Dropdown",
                  "label": "Date of Appointment",
                  "name": "date",
                  "data-source": "${data.date}",
                  "required": "${data.is_date_enabled}",
                  "enabled": "${data.is_date_enabled}",
                  "on-select-action": {
                    "name": "data_exchange",
                    "payload": {
                      "trigger": "Date_selected",
                      "Date_of_appointment": "${form.date}"
                    }
                }
              },
              {
                  "type": "Dropdown",
                  "label": "Time Slot",
                  "name": "time",
                  "data-source": "${data.time}",
                  "required": "${data.is_time_enabled}",
                  "enabled": "${data.is_time_enabled}"
              },
                
                {
                                "type": "RadioButtonsGroup",
                                "label": "Coming for Vaccination",
                                "name": "Choose_one",
                                "data-source": [
                                    {
                                        "id": "Yes",
                                        "title": "Yes"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "id": "No",
                                        "title": "No"
                                    }
                                ],
                                "required": true
                            },
                {
                  "text": "Patient Details -",
                  "type": "TextBody"
                },
                {
                  "input-type": "text",
                  "label": "Patient Name",
                  "name": "Patient_Name_319f3d",
                  "required": true,
                  "type": "TextInput"
                },
                {
                  "input-type": "text",
                  "label": "Guardian Name",
                  "name": "Guardian_Name",
                  "required": false,
                  "type": "TextInput"
                },
                {
                  "label": "Date Of Birth",
                  "name": "Date_Of_Birth_5e90dd",
                  "required": false,
                  "type": "DatePicker"
                },
                {
                  "input-type": "number",

                  "required": false,
                  "type": "TextInput"
                },
                {
                  "input-type": "email",
                  "label": "Email",
                  "name": "Email_80ff53",
                  "required": false,
                  "type": "TextInput"
                },
                {
                    "label": "Symptoms",
                    "name": "Other_Symptoms_937899",
                    "required": false,
                    "type": "TextArea"
                  },
                {
                  "input-type": "text",
                  "label": "City",
                  "name": "City",
                  "required": false,
                  "type": "TextInput"
                },
                {
                  "input-type": "text",
                  "label": "Address",
                  "name": "Address",
                  "required": false,
                  "type": "TextInput"
                },
                {
                  "label": "Continue",
                  "on-click-action": {
                    "name": "data_exchange",
                    "payload": {
                      "Date_of_appointment_0": "${form.date}",
                      "Time_Slot_1": "${form.time}",
                      "Patient_Name_2": "${form.Patient_Name_319f3d}",
                      "Guardian_Name": "${form.Guardian_Name}",
                      "Age_3": "${form.Age_8b7688}",
                      "Email_4": "${form.Email_80ff53}",
                      "Other_Symptoms_5": "${form.Other_Symptoms_937899}",
                      "Date_Of_Birth": "${form.Date_Of_Birth_5e90dd}",
                      "City": "${form.City}",
                      "Address": "${form.Address}",
                      "vaccine":"${form.Choose_one}"
                    }
                  },
                  "type": "Footer"
                }
              ],
              "name": "flow_path",
              "type": "Form"
            }
          ],
          "type": "SingleColumnLayout"

        "title": "Book Appointment"
